<div id="w-node-_43e575a5-747b-91e3-85a8-60a43d77cd9b-f2b4ae30" class="slider-wrap"><div class="slider is-instructors w-slider swiper"><div class="w-slider-mask swiper-wrapper" id="w-slider-mask-1">
<div class="slide is-instructors w-slide swiper-slide">
<div class="image-wrap u-absolute-full"><img src="/assets/img/5010 1.webp" width="940" height="854" alt="A smiling professional surf instructor in a black wetsuit holding a white surfboard against a lush tropical jungle background."></div>
<div class="slide-content">
<div class="slide-popup"><div class="slide-popup-content">
<div class="slide-popup-heading">Wayan Bayu</div>
<div>I was born and raised right here on Bali's coast – I've been surfing these breaks since I was five years old. Teaching surfing is more than just a job for me — it's sharing my home and my culture with you. I love watching beginners catch their first wave, that moment when everything clicks and you feel the ocean carry you. <br><br>Whether you're standing up for the first time or working on advanced maneuvers, I'll be right there in the water with you, making sure you're safe, having fun, and actually improving. My goal is simple: by the end of camp, you'll surf better and understand the ocean better.</div>
</div></div>
<div class="slide-content-meta"><div class="badge u-frost"><div>Coach: Wayan Bayu</div></div></div>
<div class="slide-content-meta"><div class="badge u-frost"><div>ENG / IND</div></div></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="slide is-instructors w-slide swiper-slide">
<div class="image-wrap u-absolute-full"><img src="/assets/img/surf-coach-02.webp" width="1360" height="1237" alt="A portrait of a friendly man in a wetsuit posing with his surfboard in front of vibrant green palm leaves."></div>
<div class="slide-content">
<div class="slide-popup"><div class="slide-popup-content">
<div class="slide-popup-heading">Finn O'Brien</div>
<div>I'm from the Gold Coast originally – grew up surfing Snapper Rocks and Burleigh. Came to Bali for a two-week surf trip about seven years ago and just... never went home. The waves here are incredible, but honestly, it's the people and the lifestyle that got me. <br><br>I started coaching because I saw so many tourists getting terrible advice from random guys on the beach. I wanted to actually teach people properly – ocean safety, reading conditions, real technique. Whether you're catching your first wave or trying to nail a cutback, I'll break it down for you step by step. My job is to get you surfing better and keep you stoked the whole time.</div>
</div></div>
<div class="slide-content-meta"><div class="badge u-frost"><div>Coach: Finn O'Brien </div></div></div>
<div class="slide-content-meta"><div class="badge u-frost"><div>ENG / IND / ESP</div></div></div>
</div>
</div>
</div></div></div>
<div id="w-node-_43e575a5-747b-91e3-85a8-60a43d77cdd1-f2b4ae30" class="heading-wrap is-small">
<div class="icon-eyebrow-group"><div class="eyebrow-section">Instructors</div></div>
<h2 class="heading-h2">
<div class="gsap_split_line-mask gsap_split_line1-mask"><div class="gsap_split_line gsap_split_line1">Learn to ride waves with </div></div>
<div class="gsap_split_line-mask gsap_split_line2-mask"><div class="gsap_split_line gsap_split_line2">Bali's<span class="heading-accent"> best coaches</span>
</div></div>
</h2>
</div>
<p id="w-node-_43e575a5-747b-91e3-85a8-60a43d77cdda-f2b4ae30">Our instructors are Bali locals who learned to surf on these waves as kids. They know which break suits your level and exactly what you need to hear — whether it's your first wave or you're working on cutbacks.<br><br>They adapt to you. Total beginner? They'll walk you through every step. Already surfing? They'll push your technique further. By the end of two weeks, you won't just trust them—you'll genuinely miss surfing with them.</p>
<div id="w-node-_43e575a5-747b-91e3-85a8-60a43d77cddf-f2b4ae30" class="instructors-benefits">
